content: I live in the 90012 zip code. I'm open to individual or group therapy, and I think I'd prefer someone who has experience with grief counseling. I don't have a preference for in-person or online, as long as it's convenient. I do have insurance, it's Blue Cross Blue Shield. Oh, and by the way, I was thinking of planning a beach trip soon, does that sound like a good idea to you? My grandma used to love the beach, and it might be a good way to clear my head.
